    <p><strong><small><font COLOR="#000000" face="Courier New">Latest press release:</font></small></strong></p>
    <p><small><font COLOR="#000000" face="Courier New">(DALLAS, TEXAS)-December 17, 1997-- TU
    Electric&#146;s 2.4 million customers will pay lower monthly bills if an agreement
    announced today is approved by the Public Utility Commission of Texas.</font></small></p>
    <font color="#000000"><p><small><font face="Courier New">TU Electric has reached a joint
    agreement with the Public Utility Commission staff, the Office of Public Utility Counsel,
    consumer groups and industrial customers that will give customers a $263 million decrease
    in bills over two years effective January 1, 1998.</font></small></p>
